net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6SmW4W9pwpjUnObQBOGhdL/64201223b87c9fbe8facc62b8d62085d/Doha_Debates_Second_Live_Debate_-_Image_1.jpg?w=1540&h=860&q=85&fit=pad","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6SmW4W9pwpjUnObQBOGhdL/64201223b87c9fbe8facc62b8d62085d/Doha_Debates_Second_Live_Debate_-_Image_1.jpg?w=385&h=215&q=85&fit=pad 385w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6SmW4W9pwpjUnObQBOGhdL/64201223b87c9fbe8facc62b8d62085d/Doha_Debates_Second_Live_Debate_-_Image_1.jpg?w=770&h=430&q=85&fit=pad 770w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6SmW4W9pwpjUnObQBOGhdL/64201223b87c9fbe8facc62b8d62085d/Doha_Debates_Second_Live_Debate_-_Image_1.jpg?w=1540&h=860&q=85&fit=pad 1540w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6SmW4W9pwpjUnObQBOGhdL/64201223b87c9fbe8facc62b8d62085d/Doha_Debates_Second_Live_Debate_-_Image_1.jpg?w=2283&h=1275&q=85&fit=pad 2283w","srcWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6SmW4W9pwpjUnObQBOGhdL/64201223b87c9fbe8facc62b8d62085d/Doha_Debates_Second_Live_Debate_-_Image_1.jpg?w=1540&h=860&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad","srcSetWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6SmW4W9pwpjUnObQBOGhdL/64201223b87c9fbe8facc62b8d62085d/Doha_Debates_Second_Live_Debate_-_Image_1.jpg?w=385&h=215&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad 385w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6SmW4W9pwpjUnObQBOGhdL/64201223b87c9fbe8facc62b8d62085d/Doha_Debates_Second_Live_Debate_-_Image_1.jpg?w=770&h=430&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad 770w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6SmW4W9pwpjUnObQBOGhdL/64201223b87c9fbe8facc62b8d62085d/Doha_Debates_Second_Live_Debate_-_Image_1.jpg?w=1540&h=860&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad 1540w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/6SmW4W9pwpjUnObQBOGhdL/64201223b87c9fbe8facc62b8d62085d/Doha_Debates_Second_Live_Debate_-_Image_1.jpg?w=2283&h=1275&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad 2283w","sizes":"(max-width: 1540px) 100vw, 1540px"}}}]},{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleBodyText","id":"09ea2746-be21-53c6-936d-544c404cdd1c","text":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>The debate participants included AI advocates and critics from three continents and a conflict-resolution expert, as well as debate moderator Ghida Fakhry and digital host Nelufar Hedayat. Questions to the speakers came from students in the studio audience and livestream participants around the world.</p>\n<p>The debate’s speakers were Joy Buolamwini, a Ghanaian American computer scientist and digital activist at MIT’s Media Lab; Nick Bostrom, a Swedish philosopher, bestselling author and director of Oxford University’s Future of Humanity Institute; Muthoni Wanyoike, a Kenyan data scientist and organizer at Code for Africa and Nairobi Women in Machine Learning &#x26; Data Science; Dex Torricke-Barton, a former communications executive at Facebook, Google and SpaceX, and a British bestselling author; and Govinda Clayton, the debate’s bridge-building “connector,” a conflict-resolution expert and researcher at Swiss science and technology university ETH Zurich.</p>\n<p>Joy Buolamwini highlighted that “While builders of AI systems aim to overcome human limitations, research studies and headlines continue to remind us that these systems come with risks of bias and abuse.” </p>\n<p>Nick Bostrom added, “Think about what it means to mechanize intelligence to full human level performance, and then shortly after to superhuman levels of intelligence.” </p>\n<p>Muthoni Wanyoike said \"We, as humans, have the ability to ruin the universe...or to ensure our continued existence.\" </p>"}}},{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleImageGallery","id":"961dae0f-58d5-54e4-8ac7-b5ced4b3af39","images":[{"caption":null,"image":{"id":"2732c2eb-b1ed-5b5b-ac44-fe7534da7050","title":"Doha Debates Second Live Debate - Image 2","file":{"details":{"image":{"width":2450,"height":1447}}},"sizes":{"aspectRatio":1.8666666666666667,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/2eTWni2ZVWj1N7IH9eaHb7/711b52b69ce6e28bec058a19af7c8937/Doha_Debates_Second_Live_Debate_-_Image_2.jpg?w=1120&h=600&q=85","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/2eTWni2ZVWj1N7IH9eaHb7/711b52b69ce6e28be